{"tid":492190,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)地球防衛軍5","createTime":"2017-12-07T09:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T06:35:33.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"06208bb0637477d2a3e8addb6211fb0c1f170b40","tid":492190,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:48:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">玩唔曬下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/thanksyour\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fthanksyour&d=kWCJKjsukCZ1LztrjtSwCi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=0cb463c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/thanksyour</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/AUWHIy9pR9s/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FAUWHIy9pR9s%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=643a81e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一開始，是在 2022 年的日本。在關東近郊，離市區有一段距離，必須要越過山坡才能抵達的荒地上，建立起「全地球防衛機構軍」 EDF 的基地。只看地上設施的話其實規模非常小，甚至看不出來能稱為一個基地，但其實在地下卻建設了龐大的格納倉庫。在倉庫裡收納了與和平國家－－日本完全不相配的大量武器彈藥，以及運來眾多最先進的兵器。在前幾天也空運了數十架被稱為「戰鬥框架（コンバットフレーム）」的戰鬥用步行車輛..<br />\n基地本身抱有許多問題。因為擁有過剩武裝，而讓周邊居民心生不滿，最後甚至可能發展為大型抗議運動。也因為這樣，所以基地公關部門，幾乎每個月都在舉辦活動。吸引大量參觀人士，盡全力和周邊居民交流。目前沒有任何對手，需要用上基地裡的兵器&hellip;&hellip; 所以比起強化軍力，更重要的是要爭取居民認同。但就在這時，全世界的命運出現劇烈轉折。突然出現在地球外的巨大宇宙船團，無預警地發動攻擊&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=kWCJKjsukCZ1LztrjtSwCi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=578cfc27\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=kWCJKjsukCZ1LztrjtSwCi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e1b5869a\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8c134ec1c298558c3362daba3802b3802e1fc4","tid":492190,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:20:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc267d053a3b7c79a355dc7fab878080046d612","tid":492190,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T11:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ecec904c72312cf6b9f408a51d4c47d0baa748c","tid":492190,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae9208a05c59953636bfda38e128ce7d0d67bdf","tid":492190,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:54:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144390e0627142d27073300b1e0aebcb783e1434","tid":492190,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:51:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00edd832e1fa7a483e5cd71d0704125b9b49287","tid":492190,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T08:33:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f2ca7a320844aea522e7613db3afa1